headline: Podcast: Stock Indexes Rise as Trump Boosts India Tariffs; Earnings in Focus
summary: Disney raised its annual profit forecasts for streaming and parks. Shopify reported better-than-expected results. Uber's revenue topped forecasts. Plus: The Department of Health and Human Services canceled a grant for Moderna’s bird-flu shot.
